title: 223 - What Can’t Paul Walter Hauser Do?
description: Today’s episode of The POD kicks off with a fully STACKED ship, as Tony kicks off the show listing everyone by crew title. The boys then jump right into the pod FOD, which is a folder compiled of all things around the internet. Todays FOD includes Nicks retirement from retro-bowl, does Marvel have a vendetta against fat people, the latest updates of movie and show trailers including John Which 4, House of Dragon’s, and much much more. Make sure to subscribe to youtube.come/thepodpmi to watch full episodes and don't forget to send your submissions for the Pod FOD to @ThePodPMI on twitter and instagram. We appreciate you rocking with us and we'll see you NEXT Wednesday, Cheers.
